						<div class="postbody">Enemies are just objects in most cases. Just keep track of all objects that have been killed in a 2 screen area of the screen you're on. And then also have separate objects that never ever get cleared, coins and blocks and such. That way you can have objects that respawn and objects that don't.</div>

